status/finalizer: required /
retain-until-confirmed-delete
requeue: provisioning, updating, terminating
provider states: create CREATING; update
UPDATING; delete DELETING
follow-up: create=GetWorkRequest -> GetProject;
update=GetWorkRequest -> GetProject;
delete=GetWorkRequest -> GetProject/ListProjects
confirm-delete
supported drift: defined_tags, description,
display_name, freeform_tags
